Henley Group Inc said itdeclared a special dividend distribution of one FisherScientific Group Inc share for every 16 Henley shares.    Previously, it said it would pay one fisher share for every20 outstanding, but it changed the ratio because of thereduction in its outstanding shares to 109 mln from 129 mln.    It said the distribution of about 20 pct of Fisher's commonstock will be made April six to holders of record March 26.Fisher will trade on NASDAQ under the symbol &lt;FSHG>. Reuter&#3;